    "body": "### Problem\n\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/81139999-e9dc-42f5-a271-2f576a9293bc\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. nvim --clean -u minimal.lua\n\nminimal.lua:\n\n```lua\nvim.cmd([[\nset relativenumber\n\n.a\nline 1\nline 2\nline 3\nline 4\n.\n]])\n\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(\n\t0,\n\tvim.api.nvim_create_namespace(\"test\"),\n\t0,\n\t0,\n\t{\n\t\tvirt_lines = {\n\t\t\t{{\"virt line 1\", \"NonText\"}},\n\t\t},\n\t\t-- virt_lines_above = true,\n\t\tvirt_lines_leftcol = true,\n\t}\n)\n```\n\n2. press `k`\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nrender relative line numbers correctly\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0-dev-650+gd0aedd36df\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\n6.15.2-arch1-1\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nst 0.8.5\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nst-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from repo",
